-- Ascencia to Invest $34.4 Million on Expansion, Le Mauricien Says
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-04-03T13:58:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-03/ascencia-to-invest-34-4-million-on-expansion-le-mauricien-says.html
Ascencia Ltd. (ASCE) , a Mauritian company,
plans to invest one billion rupees ($34.4 million) in extension
projects to its shopping centers in the country, Port Louis-
based Le Mauricien newspaper reported, citing the company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
